   Q. In that regard, Mr. President, I'd like to ask you about the
latest hostage situation. Do you think it was responsible for your
administration to allow a Marine lieutenant colonel, William
Higgins, to operate in southern Lebanon at a time when eight
Americans were already being held in that country and when your own
